1
00:00:51,258 --> 00:00:53,134
{\an2}<i>Aku dapat penglihatan di Amityville.</i>

2
00:00:53,969 --> 00:00:55,845
{\an2}<i>Aku dapat pertanda tentang kematianmu.</i>

3
00:00:59,015 --> 00:01:01,351
{\an2}<i>Kita melihat roh jahat yang sama.</i>

4
00:01:01,768 --> 00:01:03,937
{\an2}Ibu, siapa itu?

5
00:01:15,156 --> 00:01:18,660
{\an2}<i>Iblis di lukisanmu nyata.</i>

6
00:01:20,036 --> 00:01:23,582
{\an2}PERISTIWA BERIKUT TERJADI PADA 1952

7
00:01:27,919 --> 00:01:31,548
{\an8}BIARA ST. CARTA, RUMANIA

8
00:02:04,622 --> 00:02:08,251
{\an8}TUHAN BERAKHIR DI SINI

9
00:02:09,336 --> 00:02:11,046
{\an2}Kau yakin keputusan kita benar?

10
00:02:13,465 --> 00:02:14,924
{\an2}Tak ada pilihan.

11
00:02:33,318 --> 00:02:34,861
{\an2}Relik ini akan menyelamatkan kita?

12
00:02:38,823 --> 00:02:39,908
{\an2}Percayalah, Suster.

13
00:02:56,674 --> 00:02:59,094
{\an2}Bapa kami yang ada di surga,

14
00:02:59,677 --> 00:03:00,887
{\an2}dimuliakanlah nama-Mu.

15
00:03:01,805 --> 00:03:02,972
{\an2}Datanglah kerajaan-Mu,

16
00:03:03,264 --> 00:03:06,434
{\an2}jadilah kehendak-Mu
di atas bumi seperti di dalam surga.

17
00:03:07,769 --> 00:03:09,270
{\an2}Berilah kami rezeki pada hari ini

18
00:03:09,979 --> 00:03:11,606
{\an2}Dan ampunilah kesalahan kami

19
00:03:12,190 --> 00:03:14,526
{\an2}seperti kami pun mengampuni
yang bersalah kepada kami.

20
00:03:26,996 --> 00:03:27,997
{\an2}Ambil!

21
00:03:28,081 --> 00:03:30,708
{\an2}Iblis ini perlu wadah untuk kabur.

22
00:03:31,334 --> 00:03:33,002
{\an2}Dia akan mengincarmu.

23
00:03:33,086 --> 00:03:34,546
{\an2}Jangan biarkan dia merasukimu.

24
00:03:34,879 --> 00:03:37,590
{\an2}- Kau tahu harus berbuat apa.
- Aku tak bisa.

25
00:03:38,633 --> 00:03:40,635
{\an2}Maka Tuhan pun tak bisa menyelamatkan...

26
00:04:49,704 --> 00:04:52,707
{\an2}Ampuni aku, Bapa,
untuk dosa yang akan kuperbuat.

27
00:05:26,282 --> 00:05:27,283
{\an2}Ampuni aku, Tuhan.

28
00:06:47,238 --> 00:06:48,239
{\an2}Oh, Tuhan.

29
00:06:58,207 --> 00:07:01,002
{\an2}KOTA VATIKAN

30
00:07:02,712 --> 00:07:03,630
{\an2}Pastor Burke?

31
00:07:06,257 --> 00:07:07,133
{\an2}Uskup.

32
00:07:08,593 --> 00:07:11,346
{\an2}Kapan kali terakhir kau kemari?

33
00:07:11,512 --> 00:07:13,348
{\an2}Enam, tujuh tahun lalu?

34
00:07:14,349 --> 00:07:16,934
{\an2}Setelah tugasku sebagai pendeta
berakhir dalam perang, ya.

35
00:07:17,018 --> 00:07:20,480
{\an2}Terima kasih sudah datang
dalam waktu singkat.

36
00:07:23,650 --> 00:07:24,817
{\an2}Pastor Burke.

37
00:07:25,652 --> 00:07:26,569
{\an2}Duduklah.

38
00:07:31,783 --> 00:07:35,328
{\an2}Kami menerima kabar
bahwa seorang biarawati bunuh diri

39
00:07:35,411 --> 00:07:37,705
{\an2}di sebuah biara di gunung Rumania.

40
00:07:38,247 --> 00:07:41,209
{\an2}Bunuh diri adalah dosa yang buruk.

41
00:07:42,877 --> 00:07:45,964
{\an2}Tapi bukan alasan yang cukup kuat
untuk reuni.

42
00:07:46,381 --> 00:07:50,009
{\an2}Tapi berita ini akan menggoyahkan
argumen kita untuk tetap berpegang

43
00:07:50,093 --> 00:07:51,886
{\an2}pada iman dan Gereja.

44
00:07:52,345 --> 00:07:55,056
{\an2}- Ada yang kau rahasiakan.
- Kenapa bilang begitu?

45
00:07:55,139 --> 00:07:57,767
{\an2}Karena kita di Vatikan.

46
00:07:58,267 --> 00:07:59,727
{\an2}Biar aku perjelas, Pastor.

47
00:08:00,436 --> 00:08:05,650
{\an2}Dalam kasus langka ini sekali pun,
kami tidak percaya

48
00:08:05,733 --> 00:08:07,902
{\an2}kamilah yang menyimpan rahasia.

49
00:08:09,821 --> 00:08:12,782
{\an2}Itu dokumen perjalananmu
dan informasi kontak

50
00:08:12,865 --> 00:08:15,660
{\an2}untuk orang yang menemukan biarawati itu.

51
00:08:16,244 --> 00:08:18,871
{\an2}Dia tinggal di desa kecil dekat biara
bernama Biertan.

52
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:20,748
{\an2}Bicaralah dulu dengannya.

53
00:08:21,249 --> 00:08:24,293
{\an2}Di berkas juga ada kandidat
yang bisa bantu

54
00:08:24,377 --> 00:08:28,881
{\an2}dalam penyelidikanmu
mengingat itu adalah biara tertutup

55
00:08:28,965 --> 00:08:31,384
{\an2}dan aksesmu akan dibatasi.

56
00:08:32,969 --> 00:08:36,931
{\an2}Dia juga mengenal wilayah itu.

57
00:08:37,014 --> 00:08:37,932
{\an2}DOKUMEN PERJALANAN

58
00:08:42,770 --> 00:08:45,815
{\an2}RUMAH SAKIT SAINT VINCENTS

59
00:08:45,898 --> 00:08:48,860
{\an8}<i>Aku telah melewati</i>
<i>banyak peristiwa mengerikan.</i>

60
00:08:48,943 --> 00:08:49,819
{\an8}LONDON, INGGRIS

61
00:08:50,236 --> 00:08:53,072
{\an2}<i>Tapi tak ada yang menyiapkanku</i>
<i>untuk peristiwa ini.</i>

62
00:08:54,240 --> 00:08:57,952
{\an2}Aku hanya berharap
hewan buas itu tidak mencium bauku.

63
00:08:58,995 --> 00:09:02,540
{\an2}Namun, arah angin berubah dan...

64
00:09:06,961 --> 00:09:09,297
{\an2}Selamatkan dirimu!

65
00:09:10,506 --> 00:09:13,676
{\an2}Ibu Kepala bilang dinosaurus tidak ada.

66
00:09:14,093 --> 00:09:16,304
{\an2}Tuhan menaruh tulang mereka
untuk menguji iman kita.

67
00:09:16,596 --> 00:09:19,932
{\an2}Itu terdengar seperti tipuan, bukan?

68
00:09:20,224 --> 00:09:21,684
{\an2}Tapi mereka tidak ada di Alkitab.

69
00:09:22,018 --> 00:09:24,812
{\an2}Kau percaya penguin dan koala ada?

70
00:09:24,896 --> 00:09:27,231
{\an2}- Ya.
- Mereka juga tidak di Alkitab.

71
00:09:28,524 --> 00:09:31,402
{\an2}Alkitab adalah surat cinta Tuhan
untuk kita,

72
00:09:31,736 --> 00:09:34,447
{\an2}tapi bukan berarti
Dia tidak ingin kita bertanya

73
00:09:34,906 --> 00:09:36,741
{\an2}tentang keajaiban ciptaan-Nya.

74
00:09:36,908 --> 00:09:38,201
{\an2}Tapi Ibu Kepala bilang...

75
00:09:38,993 --> 00:09:40,912
{\an2}Tunggu. Ada sesuatu di hidungmu.

76
00:09:41,746 --> 00:09:42,580
{\an2}Itu dia.

77
00:09:51,798 --> 00:09:55,218
{\an2}- Vatikan?
- Aku juga terkejut.

78
00:09:55,718 --> 00:09:59,096
{\an2}- Aku bahkan belum bersumpah.
- Dia tahu itu.

79
00:09:59,180 --> 00:10:01,057
{\an2}Dia menunggumu di taman.

80
00:10:03,059 --> 00:10:04,852
{\an2}Dan ganti pakaianmu.

81
00:10:05,228 --> 00:10:07,230
{\an2}Ini kunjungan resmi.

82
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:13,277
{\an2}Paling lama hanya beberapa hari.

83
00:10:13,736 --> 00:10:15,154
{\an2}Kau direkomendasikan

84
00:10:15,238 --> 00:10:17,740
{\an2}karena kau mengenal wilayahnya.

85
00:10:18,074 --> 00:10:19,200
{\an2}"Wilayah"?

86
00:10:19,909 --> 00:10:21,994
{\an2}Ya. Rumania.

87
00:10:25,164 --> 00:10:26,707
{\an2}Aku belum pernah ke sana.

88
00:10:27,500 --> 00:10:29,669
{\an2}- Benarkah?
- Pasti ada kesalahan.

89
00:10:30,545 --> 00:10:33,005
{\an2}Maaf jika kedatanganmu sia-sia.

90
00:10:33,506 --> 00:10:35,341
{\an2}Tidak perlu minta maaf.

91
00:10:36,134 --> 00:10:39,470
{\an2}Setiap keputusan dari Vatikan
pasti ada tujuannya.

92
00:10:40,429 --> 00:10:43,015
{\an2}Aku yakin mereka punya alasan memilihmu.

93
00:11:09,250 --> 00:11:12,211
{\an8}BIERTAN, RUMANIA

94
00:11:17,884 --> 00:11:18,801
{\an2}Ada apa?

95
00:11:19,844 --> 00:11:21,512
{\an2}Tn. Theriault?

96
00:11:23,931 --> 00:11:24,765
{\an2}Hai.

97
00:11:26,517 --> 00:11:28,352
{\an2}Suami cemburu atau ayah yang marah?

98
00:11:29,061 --> 00:11:29,896
{\an2}Apa?

99
00:11:30,646 --> 00:11:32,815
{\an2}Biasanya satu dari dua itu

100
00:11:32,899 --> 00:11:37,320
{\an2}ketika pria tua dan gadis muda cantik

101
00:11:37,820 --> 00:11:40,865
{\an2}yang tidak begitu lugu
datang mencariku pagi-pagi begini.

102
00:11:41,490 --> 00:11:44,911
{\an2}Maaf, Tn. Theriault,
tapi kita tidak saling kenal.

103
00:11:46,454 --> 00:11:48,748
{\an2}Mungkin ini waktunya kita berkenalan.

104
00:11:50,082 --> 00:11:51,876
{\an2}Panggil aku Frenchie.

105
00:11:52,585 --> 00:11:53,544
{\an2}Seperti semua orang.

106
00:11:53,628 --> 00:11:57,423
{\an2}Tn. Theriault, kami datang karena
biarawati yang kau temukan di biara.

107
00:11:59,884 --> 00:12:00,718
{\an2}Bagaimana kau...

108
00:12:03,638 --> 00:12:04,597
{\an2}Kau pendeta?

109
00:12:05,181 --> 00:12:06,724
{\an2}Dan dia biarawati.

110
00:12:11,020 --> 00:12:12,772
{\an2}Maafkan pikiran kotorku, Suster.

111
00:12:13,731 --> 00:12:14,774
{\an2}Aku tidak tahu.

112
00:12:14,857 --> 00:12:18,069
{\an2}Tak pernah lihat biarawati tanpa jubahnya.

113
00:12:18,903 --> 00:12:20,196
{\an2}Bukannya aku menentang.

114
00:12:20,988 --> 00:12:22,073
{\an2}Permisi.

115
00:12:22,823 --> 00:12:23,950
{\an2}Tn. Theriault...

116
00:12:25,785 --> 00:12:26,827
{\an2}biaranya.

117
00:12:27,036 --> 00:12:28,079
{\an2}Jauhkah?

118
00:12:28,955 --> 00:12:32,291
{\an2}Jaraknya tidak jauh,
tapi butuh waktu untuk ke sana.

119
00:12:33,626 --> 00:12:35,836
{\an2}Kalau boleh tanya, untuk apa kau di sana?

120
00:12:36,629 --> 00:12:39,006
{\an2}Mengantar persediaan triwulanan.

121
00:12:39,090 --> 00:12:42,134
{\an2}Biara punya semacam kesepakatan...

122
00:12:43,052 --> 00:12:45,054
{\an2}dengan desa selama berabad-abad.

123
00:12:45,721 --> 00:12:48,265
{\an2}Bisa segera antar kami ke sana?

124
00:12:49,850 --> 00:12:51,060
{\an2}Kurasa tidak, Pastor.

125
00:12:52,228 --> 00:12:54,105
{\an2}Ada warga desa lain yang bisa?

126
00:12:54,188 --> 00:12:56,983
{\an2}Semua orang di desa ini
berpura-pura biara itu tidak ada.

127
00:12:57,942 --> 00:13:00,236
{\an2}Membicarakannya saja
bisa memberimu masalah.

128
00:13:01,779 --> 00:13:04,365
{\an2}Baiklah. Kau akan mengantar kami.

129
00:13:06,242 --> 00:13:10,121
{\an2}- Dengan hormat, Pastor, aku...
- Kumohon, Frenchie.

130
00:13:19,338 --> 00:13:22,049
{\an2}Kau naik pesawat dari Roma,
bus dari Bucharest.

131
00:13:23,092 --> 00:13:25,636
{\an2}Sekarang kalian berada
di Abad Pertengahan.

132
00:13:26,220 --> 00:13:27,722
{\an2}Di daerah terpencil Rumania.

133
00:13:36,313 --> 00:13:37,815
{\an2}Sekarang kau harus naik kuda.

134
00:13:39,442 --> 00:13:40,443
{\an2}Di mana barang-barangmu?

135
00:14:16,520 --> 00:14:19,148
{\an2}"Tugas pak pos."
Sembilan huruf dengan "M".

136
00:14:19,231 --> 00:14:20,274
{\an2}TEKA-TEKI SILANG

137
00:14:23,444 --> 00:14:24,445
{\an2}Mengantar.

138
00:14:25,946 --> 00:14:27,448
{\an2}Kau pintar teka-teki silang.

139
00:14:31,035 --> 00:14:33,788
{\an2}Apa yang membawa orang Prancis
ke pedesaan Rumania?

140
00:14:33,913 --> 00:14:36,957
{\an2}Aku Prancis-Kanada,
tapi jangan beri tahu siapa pun.

141
00:14:37,166 --> 00:14:38,793
{\an2}Tidak terdengar romantis.

142
00:14:39,668 --> 00:14:42,671
{\an2}Aku kemari mencari emas.
Tapi ketika bertemu orang-orang di sini,

143
00:14:42,755 --> 00:14:44,799
{\an2}aku tahu aku ditakdirkan di sini.

144
00:14:45,466 --> 00:14:47,885
{\an2}Aku ingin bantu mereka.
Apa pun yang kubisa.

145
00:14:48,636 --> 00:14:49,887
{\an2}Perbuatanmu mulia.

146
00:14:50,888 --> 00:14:52,306
{\an2}Aku tahu.

147
00:14:53,724 --> 00:14:56,727
{\an2}Katakan, Suster,
sudah berapa lama jadi biarawati?

148
00:14:58,896 --> 00:15:01,565
{\an2}Aku belum jadi biarawati.
Masih masa percobaan.

149
00:15:02,149 --> 00:15:04,110
{\an2}Belum mengambil sumpah sementaramu?

150
00:15:04,610 --> 00:15:05,653
{\an2}"Sementara"?

151
00:15:06,112 --> 00:15:09,031
{\an2}Kupikir tidak ada kata sementara
bagi biarawati.

152
00:15:09,115 --> 00:15:12,493
{\an2}Sumpah sementara bisa menyiapkanku
untuk pengabdian penuh.

153
00:15:12,576 --> 00:15:15,037
{\an2}"Bisa," Suster? Atau "akan"?

154
00:15:19,834 --> 00:15:20,876
{\an2}Ada apa?

155
00:15:22,837 --> 00:15:23,796
{\an2}Semua baik-baik saja?

156
00:15:25,089 --> 00:15:26,715
{\an2}Sisanya kita berjalan kaki.

157
00:15:27,925 --> 00:15:29,593
{\an2}Kudanya tak bisa lebih jauh lagi.

158
00:15:32,346 --> 00:15:34,181
{\an2}Mungkin kau perlu kuda baru.

159
00:15:34,515 --> 00:15:35,891
{\an2}Bukan karena kudanya, Pastor.

160
00:15:36,684 --> 00:15:39,228
{\an2}Tapi yang menanti di depan. Dia takut.

161
00:15:39,687 --> 00:15:42,773
{\an2}Penduduk bilang tempat itu terkutuk
dan kuda-kuda sependapat.

162
00:15:50,239 --> 00:15:53,868
{\an2}Kalau boleh tanya, kenapa Gereja
mengutusmu untuk tugas ini?

163
00:15:54,243 --> 00:15:56,662
{\an2}Gereja menghubungiku
jika membutuhkan penyelidik

164
00:15:56,745 --> 00:16:01,167
{\an2}untuk fenomena ganjil
yang berhubungan dengan Katolik.

165
00:16:02,209 --> 00:16:04,336
{\an2}Secara tak resmi,
disebut "pemburuan mukjizat."

166
00:16:04,795 --> 00:16:06,630
{\an2}Kupikir kita kemari
untuk kasus bunuh diri.

167
00:16:06,797 --> 00:16:09,466
{\an2}Memang, tapi itu sebagian
dari penyelidikan kita.

168
00:16:10,092 --> 00:16:13,429
{\an2}Aku juga diperintah Vatikan
untuk menentukan

169
00:16:13,512 --> 00:16:16,807
{\an2}apakah tempat itu masih... suci.

170
00:16:17,266 --> 00:16:19,852
{\an2}Aku bisa beri jawabannya sekarang, Pastor.

171
00:16:30,905 --> 00:16:32,114
{\an2}Akibat perang?

172
00:16:33,908 --> 00:16:35,201
{\an2}Pengeboman, ya.

173
00:16:35,784 --> 00:16:38,537
{\an2}Aku dengar tanahnya bergetar
selama berhari-hari.

174
00:16:39,246 --> 00:16:41,457
{\an2}Kucoba mencari informasi
tentang kastel ini,

175
00:16:41,540 --> 00:16:43,500
{\an2}tapi tak ada arsipnya di desa.

176
00:16:44,168 --> 00:16:46,086
{\an2}Dan penduduk meludah ketika kutanya.

177
00:16:46,795 --> 00:16:50,341
{\an2}- "Meludah"?
- Ya, untuk mengusir iblis.

178
00:16:51,634 --> 00:16:53,552
{\an2}Itu takhayul lama.

179
00:16:54,053 --> 00:16:57,306
{\an2}Menurutku, salib-salib
yang mengelilingi biara

180
00:16:57,389 --> 00:16:59,516
{\an2}mencegah iblis untuk keluar, bukan masuk.

181
00:17:00,976 --> 00:17:03,354
{\an2}Kau memanggil orang di dalam
ketika menemukan biarawati itu?

182
00:17:03,479 --> 00:17:05,522
{\an2}Sudah. Tak ada jawaban.

183
00:17:06,649 --> 00:17:09,568
{\an2}Tapi, selama dua tahun
mengantar persediaan,

184
00:17:10,486 --> 00:17:12,154
{\an2}dia orang pertama yang kulihat.

185
00:17:16,325 --> 00:17:19,411
{\an2}Frenchie, saat menemukan biarawati itu,
apa yang kau lakukan?

186
00:17:19,954 --> 00:17:22,164
{\an2}Kupindahkan untuk melindungi
jasadnya dari elemen.

187
00:17:22,248 --> 00:17:23,666
{\an2}Kau pindahkan ke mana?

188
00:17:24,083 --> 00:17:27,294
{\an2}Gudang es.
Tempat aku meninggalkan kiriman.

189
00:17:30,172 --> 00:17:34,635
{\an2}Saat menemukannya,
kupikir dengan memindahkannya ke situ

190
00:17:34,718 --> 00:17:36,929
{\an2}bisa menolong mengawetkannya.

191
00:17:48,440 --> 00:17:49,525
{\an8}Silakan.

192
00:18:16,844 --> 00:18:19,555
{\an2}- Satu hal lagi, Pastor.
- Apa?

193
00:18:20,598 --> 00:18:22,266
{\an2}Aku tidak meninggalkannya seperti itu.

194
00:18:24,143 --> 00:18:25,144
{\an2}Maksudmu?

195
00:18:25,519 --> 00:18:29,648
{\an2}Dia terbaring saat kutinggal di sini.
Bukan duduk begitu.

196
00:18:48,042 --> 00:18:53,881
{\an2}Memang ada jasad yang menyentak
atau jadi posisi duduk,

197
00:18:53,964 --> 00:18:55,299
{\an2}tak lama setelah meninggal.

198
00:18:55,674 --> 00:18:58,552
{\an2}Tapi entah sudah berapa lama
dia meninggal saat kutemukan.

199
00:18:58,636 --> 00:18:59,887
{\an2}Kau tidak membantu.

200
00:19:00,512 --> 00:19:01,430
{\an2}Maaf.

201
00:19:12,441 --> 00:19:13,359
{\an2}Pastor, apa itu?

202
00:19:13,442 --> 00:19:15,819
{\an2}Sepertinya semacam kunci.

203
00:19:24,286 --> 00:19:27,331
{\an2}Biarawati masuk dari pintu itu
untuk ambil persediaan.

204
00:19:28,499 --> 00:19:30,000
{\an2}Agar tak perlu keluar kastel.

205
00:19:33,295 --> 00:19:35,255
{\an2}Kita beri dia pemakaman yang layak.

206
00:19:37,758 --> 00:19:41,887
{\an2}Atas nama Bapa, Anak, dan Roh Kudus. Amin.

207
00:19:52,856 --> 00:19:56,902
{\an2}Itu umum saat terjadi wabah.
Saat orang takut dikubur hidup-hidup.

208
00:19:57,069 --> 00:20:00,239
{\an2}Jika kau bernasib buruk
dan terjadi kepadamu,

209
00:20:00,322 --> 00:20:04,034
{\an2}kau bisa bunyikan belnya
agar orang di atas tahu...

210
00:20:04,618 --> 00:20:05,828
{\an2}mereka buat kesalahan.

211
00:20:05,911 --> 00:20:07,913
{\an2}Berada di sini sudah salah.

212
00:20:27,891 --> 00:20:29,309
{\an2}Aku menemukannya di situ.

213
00:21:10,768 --> 00:21:13,770
{\an2}Bagaimana mungkin?
Sudah berminggu-minggu.

214
00:21:13,854 --> 00:21:16,607
{\an2}Sudah kubilang. Tempat ini...

215
00:21:17,691 --> 00:21:19,818
{\an2}Apa kebalikan dari mukjizat, Pastor?

216
00:23:05,924 --> 00:23:06,925
{\an2}Halo?

217
00:23:10,762 --> 00:23:13,181
{\an2}Maaf kami tak mengabari kedatangan kami.

218
00:23:17,853 --> 00:23:18,854
{\an2}Halo?

219
00:23:21,064 --> 00:23:23,025
{\an2}Apa maumu?

220
00:23:25,277 --> 00:23:27,154
{\an2}Aku Pastor Anthony Burke.

221
00:23:27,779 --> 00:23:29,615
{\an2}Ini Suster Irene.

222
00:23:31,074 --> 00:23:32,659
{\an2}Kau Suster Kepala?

223
00:23:33,535 --> 00:23:34,661
{\an2}Benar.

224
00:23:36,622 --> 00:23:39,374
{\an2}Kau belum bersumpah.

225
00:23:42,252 --> 00:23:43,086
{\an2}Belum.

226
00:23:43,629 --> 00:23:45,881
{\an2}- Tolonglah...
- Kenapa kau di sini, Pastor?

227
00:23:46,381 --> 00:23:48,175
{\an2}Kami datang mewakili Roma,

228
00:23:48,258 --> 00:23:50,844
{\an2}untuk menyelidiki
kematian baru-baru ini di biaramu.

229
00:23:51,511 --> 00:23:53,138
{\an2}"Kematian baru-baru ini"?

230
00:23:53,972 --> 00:23:55,307
{\an2}Salah satu biarawatimu.

231
00:23:57,434 --> 00:24:00,812
{\an2}Kutemukan di luar. Tergantung di lehernya.

232
00:24:02,397 --> 00:24:03,565
{\an8}Begitu?

233
00:24:06,193 --> 00:24:09,821
{\an8}Dan menurutmu pantas untuk menguburnya?

234
00:24:13,116 --> 00:24:16,244
{\an2}Bisa tinggalkan kami sebentar?

235
00:24:26,713 --> 00:24:28,882
{\an2}Pergilah bersamanya.

236
00:24:30,300 --> 00:24:32,886
{\an2}Kau tidak tahu
tentang kematian biarawati itu?

237
00:24:34,346 --> 00:24:37,724
{\an2}Roma mencemaskan keamanan
dan kesejahteraan biaramu.

238
00:24:38,350 --> 00:24:39,601
{\an2}Aku ingin bicara dengan suster

239
00:24:39,685 --> 00:24:42,354
{\an2}agar aku bisa berikan jaminanku
kepada Gereja.

240
00:24:43,063 --> 00:24:46,650
{\an2}Aku bisa berikan jaminan yang kau cari.

241
00:24:46,775 --> 00:24:48,819
{\an2}Itu tidak cukup.

242
00:24:50,362 --> 00:24:55,951
{\an2}Mereka akan mengirim petugas gereja
lainnya yang kurang diplomatis.

243
00:24:56,034 --> 00:24:57,911
{\an2}Ya, Pastor.

244
00:24:58,578 --> 00:25:04,626
{\an2}Tapi gerbang akan ditutup sebentar lagi
untuk doa malam.

245
00:25:04,710 --> 00:25:09,923
{\an2}Dilanjutkan dengan Saat Teduh
yang berakhir pagi hari.

246
00:25:10,090 --> 00:25:15,762
{\an2}Kembalilah besok dan kau akan temukan
jawaban yang kau cari.

247
00:25:16,430 --> 00:25:21,852
{\an2}Ada pondok di biara.
Kau boleh menginap di sana.

248
00:25:28,567 --> 00:25:29,776
{\an2}Terima kasih.

249
00:25:41,204 --> 00:25:45,375
{\an2}Kenapa tak bisa bicara dengan para suster
sekarang? Kenapa harus besok pagi?

250
00:25:45,792 --> 00:25:48,712
{\an2}Para suster bersumpah diam
dari matahari terbenam sampai terbit

251
00:25:48,795 --> 00:25:50,172
{\an2}yang harus dihormati.

252
00:25:50,797 --> 00:25:52,466
{\an2}Sebaiknya kau pulang.

253
00:25:52,883 --> 00:25:55,969
{\an2}Kau tak ingin di jalanan itu
pada malam hari.

254
00:25:57,721 --> 00:25:59,890
{\an2}Lebih baik di jalanan
ketimbang di sini, Pastor.

255
00:26:01,266 --> 00:26:03,977
{\an2}Kami akan baik-baik saja, Nak.
Kembalilah beberapa hari lagi.

256
00:26:04,811 --> 00:26:06,938
{\an2}Itu cukup waktu bagi kami
untuk dapat jawaban.

257
00:26:10,025 --> 00:26:11,151
{\an2}Ya, Pastor.

258
00:26:19,785 --> 00:26:22,621
{\an2}<i>Senang bertemu denganmu, Sayang</i>

259
00:26:54,319 --> 00:26:55,278
{\an2}Halo?

260
00:27:21,721 --> 00:27:22,556
{\an2}Hei.

261
00:27:23,640 --> 00:27:24,516
{\an2}Hei!

262
00:29:01,279 --> 00:29:03,448
{\an2}Kuambil... ini.

263
00:29:09,913 --> 00:29:10,872
{\an2}Baik.

264
00:29:12,457 --> 00:29:13,416
{\an2}Baiklah.

265
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:44,948
{\an2}Pastor?

266
00:29:45,782 --> 00:29:47,909
{\an2}Tadi kau bilang "pemburuan mukjizat".

267
00:29:48,410 --> 00:29:49,327
{\an2}Itu...

268
00:29:50,495 --> 00:29:52,163
{\an2}Itu peran yang kau inginkan?

269
00:29:52,247 --> 00:29:53,123
{\an2}Tidak.

270
00:29:54,290 --> 00:29:55,250
{\an2}Tentu tidak.

271
00:29:56,209 --> 00:30:00,588
{\an2}Aku salah satu dari sedikit orang
yang Gereja andalkan untuk...

272
00:30:02,549 --> 00:30:03,925
{\an2}menyelidiki...

273
00:30:06,011 --> 00:30:07,387
{\an2}persoalan ganjil.

274
00:30:07,721 --> 00:30:09,055
{\an2}Kau kenal Uskup Forne?

275
00:30:10,015 --> 00:30:12,642
{\an2}- Bagaimana kau...
- Dia pernah menolongku dulu.

276
00:30:13,351 --> 00:30:15,478
{\an2}Aku dapat serangkaian penglihatan
saat kecil.

277
00:30:16,312 --> 00:30:18,732
{\an2}Ayahku percaya
aku menderita gangguan jiwa.

278
00:30:19,357 --> 00:30:21,067
{\an2}Atau lebih buruk, pembohong.

279
00:30:22,277 --> 00:30:24,320
{\an2}Tapi kabar tentang penglihatanku
didengar Gereja.

280
00:30:24,404 --> 00:30:25,989
{\an2}Kardinal Conroy, khususnya.

281
00:30:26,072 --> 00:30:28,074
{\an2}Dia mengutus Uskup Forne untuk menemuiku.

282
00:30:28,408 --> 00:30:29,951
{\an2}Apa penglihatanmu?

283
00:30:33,371 --> 00:30:34,330
{\an2}Ada banyak.

284
00:30:35,498 --> 00:30:37,083
{\an2}Tak pernah terulang yang sama.

285
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:40,420
{\an2}Tapi, setiap kali
satu penglihatan berakhir,

286
00:30:40,503 --> 00:30:42,839
{\an2}pikiran yang sama muncul di benakku.

287
00:30:43,173 --> 00:30:45,216
{\an2}Yaitu... apa?

288
00:30:47,218 --> 00:30:48,762
{\an2}"Maria menunjukkan jalan."

289
00:30:58,938 --> 00:31:00,190
{\an2}Ada apa, Pastor?

290
00:31:02,150 --> 00:31:08,907
{\an2}Aku memikirkan insiden serupa di Prancis.
Ketika perang.

291
00:31:09,324 --> 00:31:12,285
{\an2}<i>Aku ditugaskan di sana. Dekat Lyon.</i>

292
00:31:13,411 --> 00:31:15,872
{\an2}Aku diminta menyelidiki
anak yang dapat penglihatan.

293
00:31:19,334 --> 00:31:20,919
{\an2}Tapi, berbeda dengan kasusmu,

294
00:31:22,670 --> 00:31:24,964
{\an2}setelah evaluasi yang cermat...

295
00:31:28,718 --> 00:31:30,595
{\an2}kuputuskan bahwa dia kerasukan,

296
00:31:31,304 --> 00:31:34,224
{\an2}dan aku bertindak sesuai hukum Gereja.

297
00:31:36,351 --> 00:31:39,187
{\an2}Astaga. Daniel...

298
00:31:44,150 --> 00:31:45,860
{\an2}Apa yang mereka perbuat kepadamu?

299
00:31:56,079 --> 00:31:57,372
{\an2}Berhasilkah?

300
00:31:58,373 --> 00:31:59,999
{\an2}Gereja pikir begitu.

301
00:32:01,418 --> 00:32:03,878
{\an2}Mereka percaya iblisnya telah diusir.

302
00:32:05,672 --> 00:32:06,840
{\an2}Tapi kau tidak.

303
00:32:09,384 --> 00:32:11,136
{\an2}Pangeran Yang Termulia...

304
00:32:12,053 --> 00:32:16,349
{\an2}dari Pasukan Surgawi,
Santo Michael, malaikat agung...

305
00:32:24,107 --> 00:32:25,316
{\an2}Tolong aku, Pastor!

306
00:32:25,775 --> 00:32:31,030
{\an2}Tolonglah Daniel, yang Tuhan ciptakan
sesuai gambaran-Nya!

307
00:32:32,198 --> 00:32:34,659
{\an2}- Lihatlah Salib Tuhan!
- Kenapa tidak menolongku?

308
00:32:34,742 --> 00:32:35,869
{\an2}Kau kuasa jahat!

309
00:32:43,668 --> 00:32:47,130
{\an2}Daniel mengalami cedera parah
akibat eksorsis.

310
00:32:47,714 --> 00:32:49,507
{\an2}<i>Dia tidak pulih dari cederanya.</i>

311
00:32:50,133 --> 00:32:52,177
{\an2}Daniel, maafkan aku.

312
00:33:01,060 --> 00:33:03,271
{\an2}Dia meninggal beberapa hari kemudian.

313
00:33:07,901 --> 00:33:11,571
{\an2}Terkadang aku berpikir
apa aku terlalu bersikeras dengan tekadku.

314
00:33:13,573 --> 00:33:14,699
{\an2}Itu sebuah teka-teki.

315
00:35:21,451 --> 00:35:22,327
{\an2}Pastor.

316
00:36:24,305 --> 00:36:25,306
{\an2}Pastor.

317
00:36:34,023 --> 00:36:34,941
{\an2}Daniel?

318
00:36:54,669 --> 00:36:57,672
{\an2}Tunggu! Tidak! Tolong!

319
00:36:58,589 --> 00:37:01,175
{\an2}Tolong! Tidak!

320
00:37:01,634 --> 00:37:07,598
{\an2}DI SINI BERBARING
PASTOR ANTHONY BURKE

321
00:38:17,376 --> 00:38:18,878
{\an2}Tolong!

322
00:38:21,672 --> 00:38:22,507
{\an2}Siapa saja.

323
00:40:13,951 --> 00:40:17,038
{\an2}Tolong! Suster Irene! Tolong!

324
00:40:19,749 --> 00:40:22,501
{\an2}Pastor!

325
00:40:26,422 --> 00:40:27,423
{\an2}Pastor?

326
00:40:39,143 --> 00:40:40,144
{\an2}Pastor?

327
00:41:17,765 --> 00:41:19,392
{\an2}Tolong!

328
00:41:21,686 --> 00:41:22,645
{\an2}Tolong aku!

329
00:41:37,535 --> 00:41:39,453
{\an2}- Pastor?
- Suster?

330
00:41:39,537 --> 00:41:40,496
{\an2}Suster Irene!

331
00:41:40,579 --> 00:41:42,289
{\an2}Pastor, aku bisa mendengarmu!

332
00:41:43,416 --> 00:41:44,375
{\an2}Aku di sini.

333
00:41:45,793 --> 00:41:47,670
{\an2}Syukurlah. Terima kasih.

334
00:42:52,485 --> 00:42:53,444
{\an2}Cepat!

335
00:42:58,365 --> 00:42:59,575
{\an2}Tunggu!

336
00:43:17,176 --> 00:43:18,928
{\an2}Terima kasih, Suster.

337
00:43:27,478 --> 00:43:30,106
{\an2}Bagaimana kau bisa di situ?
Tanahnya tertutup.

338
00:43:30,856 --> 00:43:33,484
{\an2}Ada kuasa jahat di tempat ini.

339
00:43:41,617 --> 00:43:44,203
{\an2}Mungkin buku-buku itu
bisa memberikan jawaban.

340
00:43:48,791 --> 00:43:51,418
{\an2}Darahnya bertambah. Bagaimana mungkin?

341
00:43:52,128 --> 00:43:53,212
{\an2}Teka-teki lain.

342
00:44:09,019 --> 00:44:09,854
{\an2}Suster Kepala?

343
00:44:12,898 --> 00:44:17,194
{\an2}Sesuai permintaan,
kami mau bicara dengan para biarawati.

344
00:44:25,786 --> 00:44:29,164
{\an2}Kurasa ini undangan untuk masuk.

345
00:44:29,915 --> 00:44:31,125
{\an2}Aku akan cari Suster Kepala.

346
00:44:32,501 --> 00:44:33,544
{\an2}Bawa ini.

347
00:44:35,880 --> 00:44:37,798
{\an2}Selidikilah.

348
00:44:38,340 --> 00:44:40,759
{\an2}Jelas itu penting bagi almarhum.

349
00:44:41,802 --> 00:44:44,263
{\an2}Suster. Hati-hati.

350
00:44:45,222 --> 00:44:46,265
{\an2}Baik, Pastor.

351
00:45:09,121 --> 00:45:10,039
{\an2}Halo?

352
00:45:11,415 --> 00:45:12,249
{\an2}Tunggu!

353
00:46:15,020 --> 00:46:16,355
{\an2}Suster?

354
00:46:39,628 --> 00:46:40,587
{\an2}Suster!

355
00:46:41,964 --> 00:46:44,425
{\an2}Kita tak boleh berhenti berdoa
sedetik pun.

356
00:46:45,175 --> 00:46:47,970
{\an2}Biara ini terus berdoa
selama berabad-abad.

357
00:46:48,220 --> 00:46:50,806
{\an2}Para suster berdoa bergantian
untuk tetap berjaga.

358
00:46:50,973 --> 00:46:52,683
{\an2}Maaf aku mengganggunya.

359
00:46:52,808 --> 00:46:56,478
{\an2}Suster Ruth menghadapi lebih dari
orang menyelinap di belakangnya.

360
00:46:57,229 --> 00:46:59,857
{\an2}Aku Suster Oana.
Kami dikabari tentang kedatanganmu.

361
00:47:00,357 --> 00:47:01,859
{\an2}Ikuti aku.

362
00:47:10,826 --> 00:47:15,205
{\an8}BERUANG HITAM

363
00:47:20,544 --> 00:47:21,420
{\an2}Apa?

364
00:47:24,048 --> 00:47:27,968
{\an2}Satu lagi.
Kuberi tahu Luca minumannya gratis.

365
00:47:31,221 --> 00:47:34,516
{\an2}- Kenapa dia tutup cerminnya?
- Tradisi di sini ketika ada orang mati.

366
00:47:34,600 --> 00:47:37,644
{\an2}Cermin ditutup agar almarhum
tidak melihat pantulannya

367
00:47:37,728 --> 00:47:39,063
{\an2}dan menjadi hantu.

368
00:47:39,980 --> 00:47:41,356
{\an2}Ada yang meninggal?

369
00:47:41,482 --> 00:47:45,152
{\an2}Kau tak dengar? Putri Luca bunuh diri.

370
00:47:48,530 --> 00:47:51,575
{\an2}Sulit dipercaya. Dia masih kecil.

371
00:47:52,701 --> 00:47:56,246
{\an2}Usia 12 tahun. Gantung diri di lumbung.

372
00:47:57,956 --> 00:48:00,542
{\an2}Gantung diri? Kenapa?

373
00:48:01,126 --> 00:48:03,837
{\an2}Kenapa panen Addi Constantine menjadi abu?

374
00:48:04,630 --> 00:48:06,590
{\an2}Kenapa Stefan kecil jadi buta?

375
00:48:07,007 --> 00:48:09,426
{\an2}Karena tempat itu. Biara itu.

376
00:48:10,719 --> 00:48:14,389
{\an2}Iblis yang ada di sana menyusup keluar
dan meracuni kita.

377
00:48:17,851 --> 00:48:20,229
{\an2}Dua orang yang kau antar ke sana kemarin.

378
00:48:21,313 --> 00:48:23,607
{\an2}- Siapa mereka?
- Pendeta dan biarawati.

379
00:48:24,191 --> 00:48:25,400
{\an2}Mereka masih di sana?

380
00:48:27,111 --> 00:48:29,196
{\an2}Ya. Besok kujemput.

381
00:48:29,780 --> 00:48:32,074
{\an2}Baru-baru ini
kau menemukan jasad di sana, benar?

382
00:48:32,157 --> 00:48:33,867
{\an2}Ya, Grigore.

383
00:48:33,951 --> 00:48:37,371
{\an2}Aku yakin kau akan menemukan dua lagi.

384
00:48:50,843 --> 00:48:56,098
{\an2}Dan dari tanah dibentuklah
segala binatang hutan

385
00:48:56,181 --> 00:48:58,892
{\an2}dan segala burung di udara.

386
00:49:00,602 --> 00:49:06,024
{\an2}Apa pun sebutan manusia
untuk makhluk iblis, demikianlah namanya.

387
00:49:09,736 --> 00:49:10,571
{\an2}Valak.

388
00:49:12,281 --> 00:49:13,574
{\an2}Yang Cemar.

389
00:49:14,449 --> 00:49:15,492
{\an2}Yang Najis.

390
00:49:16,869 --> 00:49:18,412
{\an2}Panglima para Ular.

391
00:49:29,339 --> 00:49:30,340
{\an2}Suster!

392
00:49:34,303 --> 00:49:35,512
{\an2}Suster Irene!

393
00:49:41,810 --> 00:49:45,480
{\an2}Kematian Suster Victoria
adalah tragedi bagi biara ini...

394
00:49:46,565 --> 00:49:48,567
{\an2}tapi kami masih merasakan kehadirannya.

395
00:49:49,151 --> 00:49:51,445
{\an2}Dia yang paling berbakti di antara kami.

396
00:49:55,490 --> 00:49:56,742
{\an2}Permisi, Suster.

397
00:50:10,714 --> 00:50:11,840
{\an2}Suster Vic...

398
00:50:19,723 --> 00:50:23,352
{\an2}Maaf, kami sangat menjaga privasi kami.

399
00:50:23,810 --> 00:50:26,480
{\an2}Beberapa suster lebih suka
aku tidak bicara denganmu.

400
00:50:27,898 --> 00:50:29,775
{\an2}Kami hargai kesediaanmu.

401
00:50:30,484 --> 00:50:34,446
{\an2}Suster Oana, bisa ceritakan
tentang sejarah biara ini?

402
00:50:37,491 --> 00:50:40,118
{\an2}Biara ini dibangun seorang adipati
pada Abad Pertengahan.

403
00:50:42,162 --> 00:50:43,705
{\an2}<i>Adipati Saint Carta.</i>

404
00:50:44,831 --> 00:50:48,252
{\an2}<i>Dia menulis banyak naskah</i>
<i>tentang sihir dan ritual,</i>

405
00:50:48,335 --> 00:50:50,504
{\an2}untuk memanggil kekuatan dari neraka.

406
00:50:51,380 --> 00:50:55,550
{\an2}Neraka menggunakannya
untuk membuka gerbang agar iblis

407
00:50:55,634 --> 00:50:57,094
{\an2}<i>dapat berjalan di tengah kita.</i>

408
00:51:12,150 --> 00:51:13,986
{\an2}<i>Namun Gereja menyerbu kastel itu.</i>

409
00:51:19,283 --> 00:51:22,786
{\an2}Mereka menutup gerbangnya
menggunakan relik kuno

410
00:51:23,620 --> 00:51:25,998
{\an2}<i>berisi darah Yesus Kristus.</i>

411
00:51:30,836 --> 00:51:34,881
{\an2}<i>Gereja merebut kastel itu</i>
<i>dan doa tanpa henti kami dimulai</i>

412
00:51:34,965 --> 00:51:37,843
{\an2}<i>untuk mengamankan biara dan menahan iblis.</i>

413
00:51:37,926 --> 00:51:41,763
{\an2}<i>Selama berabad-abad itu berhasil</i>
<i>dan iblis tak bisa masuk...</i>

414
00:51:42,723 --> 00:51:45,350
{\an2}<i>sampai bom peperangan mengguncang biara...</i>

415
00:51:46,518 --> 00:51:49,521
{\an2}dan iblis menemukan jalan lain
untuk membuka gerbang.

416
00:51:50,605 --> 00:51:54,192
{\an2}Suster Oana, semalam di kapel,

417
00:51:54,776 --> 00:51:55,944
{\an2}ada biarawati.

418
00:51:57,404 --> 00:52:02,242
{\an2}Dia sama sekali tidak terasa suci.

419
00:52:03,493 --> 00:52:04,870
{\an2}Kau juga melihatnya?

420
00:52:06,330 --> 00:52:08,665
{\an2}Aku melihatnya berjalan di lorong
pada malam hari.

421
00:52:09,249 --> 00:52:10,584
{\an2}<i>Kami semua melihatnya.</i>

422
00:52:11,460 --> 00:52:13,795
{\an2}<i>Dia terlihat seperti kami,</i>
<i>tapi bukan salah satu dari kami.</i>

423
00:52:14,212 --> 00:52:15,505
{\an2}Itu sesuatu yang jahat.

424
00:52:15,964 --> 00:52:19,468
{\an2}Dia berubah wujud untuk menipu kami
dan memangsa kelemahan kami.

425
00:52:19,551 --> 00:52:21,887
{\an2}Dia berwujud biarawati agar bisa menyamar

426
00:52:21,970 --> 00:52:23,513
{\an2}<i>sampai dia merusak kami semua.</i>

427
00:52:24,097 --> 00:52:27,100
{\an2}Aku takut kehadirannya
menandakan gerbangnya dibuka kembali.

428
00:52:27,893 --> 00:52:30,062
{\an2}Dia membuat Suster Victoria
melakukan dosa terbesar.

429
00:52:30,145 --> 00:52:31,313
{\an2}Suster Oana.

430
00:52:35,192 --> 00:52:37,527
{\an2}Suster Ruth hampir selesai dengan doanya.

431
00:52:38,737 --> 00:52:41,531
{\an2}- Giliranmu berdoa.
- Baik, Suster.

432
00:52:48,413 --> 00:52:50,123
{\an2}Kau belum bersumpah?

433
00:52:50,749 --> 00:52:53,418
{\an2}- Belum.
- Maka tempat ini bukan untukmu.

434
00:52:54,086 --> 00:52:56,963
{\an2}- Kau harus pergi. Sekarang.
- Tidak bisa.

435
00:52:58,173 --> 00:53:00,926
{\an2}Gerbang ditutup.
Kau harus di sini sampai gerbang dibuka.

436
00:53:01,051 --> 00:53:05,097
{\an2}- Kapan?
- Matahari terbit. Kau harus menginap.

437
00:53:16,358 --> 00:53:17,442
{\an2}Suster Irene.

438
00:53:31,373 --> 00:53:32,499
{\an2}Selamat malam, Suster.

439
00:53:33,083 --> 00:53:34,084
{\an2}Suster, tunggu.

440
00:53:35,043 --> 00:53:36,044
{\an2}Ya?

441
00:53:38,004 --> 00:53:40,424
{\an2}Suster Victoria memegang ini
ketika dia meninggal.

442
00:53:41,716 --> 00:53:43,135
{\an2}Kau tahu ini untuk apa?

443
00:53:43,802 --> 00:53:44,719
{\an2}Tidak.

444
00:53:49,683 --> 00:53:51,351
{\an2}Aku harus pergi berdoa.

445
00:54:29,139 --> 00:54:30,182
{\an2}Di mana kau?

446
00:54:32,184 --> 00:54:36,271
{\an2}Kau tak akan menemukan
jalan masuk lain, Pastor.

447
00:54:38,106 --> 00:54:39,316
{\an2}Suster Kepala?

448
00:54:50,785 --> 00:54:54,581
{\an2}Apa yang membuatmu cemas?

449
00:55:00,253 --> 00:55:05,759
{\an2}Ada sesuatu yang sangat salah
dengan tempat ini, Suster Kepala.

450
00:55:07,093 --> 00:55:12,641
{\an2}Seperti banyak tempat di dunia,
biara ini punya sejarah panjang.

451
00:55:13,183 --> 00:55:17,771
{\an2}Tidak seluruhnya baik, tapi kami bertobat.

452
00:55:19,314 --> 00:55:23,818
{\an2}Biarawati itu, kutemukan kunci
dalam genggamannya.

453
00:55:23,902 --> 00:55:25,612
{\an2}Kuncinya untuk membuka apa?

454
00:55:26,154 --> 00:55:28,698
{\an2}Sudah terlambat, Pastor.

455
00:55:28,782 --> 00:55:32,244
{\an2}Suster Irene tak bisa ditolong.

456
00:55:40,585 --> 00:55:41,711
{\an2}Suster Kepala?

457
00:55:52,305 --> 00:55:53,306
{\an2}Suster Kepala?

458
00:56:38,018 --> 00:56:39,519
{\an2}<i>Suster Irene.</i>

459
00:56:40,103 --> 00:56:41,646
{\an2}<i>Maria menunjukkan jalan.</i>

460
00:56:42,188 --> 00:56:45,275
{\an2}<i>Maria menunjukkan jalan.</i>

461
00:57:14,679 --> 00:57:15,805
{\an2}Siapa kau?

462
00:58:13,738 --> 00:58:14,823
{\an2}Tuhan menolongmu.

463
00:58:40,640 --> 00:58:42,767
{\an2}<i>Suster, kemarilah.</i>

464
00:58:44,144 --> 00:58:45,395
{\an2}Suster Oana?

465
00:59:52,045 --> 00:59:54,756
{\an2}TUHAN BERAKHIR DI SINI

466
01:00:17,195 --> 01:00:18,196
{\an2}Oh, Tuhan.

467
01:01:50,914 --> 01:01:51,915
{\an2}Diam.

468
01:01:58,796 --> 01:02:00,423
{\an2}Iblis makin kuat.

469
01:02:00,924 --> 01:02:03,176
{\an2}Ambil barang-barangmu
dan temui aku di kapel, Suster.

470
01:02:03,259 --> 01:02:05,094
{\an2}Hanya dengan doa
kita bisa melewati malam ini.

471
01:02:06,137 --> 01:02:08,389
{\an2}Pergilah.

472
01:02:10,558 --> 01:02:11,559
{\an2}Sekarang.

473
01:02:54,018 --> 01:02:55,019
{\an2}Halo?

474
01:03:36,936 --> 01:03:38,187
{\an2}Suster Oana?

475
01:03:49,073 --> 01:03:51,367
{\an2}<i>Sudah berapa lama aku mati, Pastor?</i>

476
01:03:54,287 --> 01:03:55,621
{\an2}<i>Berapa lama?</i>

477
01:04:00,585 --> 01:04:01,878
{\an2}Daniel?

478
01:04:02,754 --> 01:04:03,880
{\an2}Maafkan aku.

479
01:04:06,883 --> 01:04:08,926
{\an2}Kenapa kau tidak menolongku?

480
01:04:53,930 --> 01:04:55,807
{\an2}Kita harus berdoa, sekarang.

481
01:04:56,099 --> 01:04:58,768
{\an2}Apa pun yang terjadi,
apa pun yang kau lihat atau dengar,

482
01:04:58,851 --> 01:05:01,479
{\an2}terus arahkan matamu ke depan
dan jangan berhenti berdoa.

483
01:06:16,053 --> 01:06:17,805
{\an2}MENGANTAR

484
01:06:17,889 --> 01:06:21,225
{\an2}<i>Itu pintu yang digunakan biarawati</i>
<i>untuk ambil persediaan.</i>

485
01:06:21,392 --> 01:06:23,102
{\an2}<i>Agar tak perlu keluar kastel.</i>

486
01:07:16,239 --> 01:07:17,323
{\an2}Tidak.

487
01:07:37,426 --> 01:07:39,011
{\an2}Ya Tuhan.

488
01:07:40,513 --> 01:07:41,639
{\an2}Frenchie!

489
01:07:41,722 --> 01:07:43,099
{\an2}Kupikir kau butuh bantuan.

490
01:07:45,476 --> 01:07:46,477
{\an2}Terima kasih.

491
01:07:47,186 --> 01:07:52,525
{\an2}Tapi tolonglah, lain kali,
tolong gunakan senapan.

492
01:07:53,651 --> 01:07:55,820
{\an2}Kusimpan untuk keadaan darurat.

493
01:08:48,497 --> 01:08:49,498
{\an2}Suster!

494
01:08:51,792 --> 01:08:53,044
{\an2}Suster Irene!

495
01:08:55,129 --> 01:08:56,297
{\an2}Pastor Burke.

496
01:09:04,430 --> 01:09:07,016
{\an2}Itu Pastor Burke. Dia akan menolong kita.

497
01:09:08,392 --> 01:09:09,644
{\an2}Suster!

498
01:09:17,902 --> 01:09:19,111
{\an2}Suster Irene!

499
01:09:24,033 --> 01:09:25,409
{\an2}Syukurlah, Pastor.

500
01:09:25,493 --> 01:09:26,660
{\an2}Kau baik-baik saja, Suster?

501
01:09:28,245 --> 01:09:29,163
{\an2}Frenchie?

502
01:09:29,997 --> 01:09:31,082
{\an2}Apa yang terjadi?

503
01:09:31,165 --> 01:09:35,002
{\an2}Kami sedang berdoa, kami semua.

504
01:09:35,127 --> 01:09:38,672
{\an2}Doa tanpa henti,
itulah yang menahan iblis itu selama ini.

505
01:09:40,007 --> 01:09:41,217
{\an2}Siapa yang berdoa?

506
01:09:41,926 --> 01:09:43,928
{\an2}Kami semua. Para biarawati lain.

507
01:10:06,575 --> 01:10:07,868
{\an2}Tadi mereka di sini.

508
01:10:08,661 --> 01:10:10,579
{\an2}Mereka sedang berdoa ketika kami diserang.

509
01:10:14,166 --> 01:10:16,335
{\an2}- Para biarawati memperingatkanku.
- Penglihatan.

510
01:10:16,419 --> 01:10:17,753
{\an2}Terasa begitu nyata.

511
01:11:09,889 --> 01:11:11,140
{\an2}Tak ada yang tersisa.

512
01:11:14,852 --> 01:11:16,562
{\an2}Kita sudah dapat jawaban, Pastor.

513
01:11:18,189 --> 01:11:21,609
{\an2}Seperti dugaan sejak awal,
tempat ini tidak lagi suci.

514
01:11:28,115 --> 01:11:30,367
{\an2}Pastor. Ya Tuhan...

515
01:11:37,041 --> 01:11:38,459
{\an2}Pastor, kita harus berbuat apa?

516
01:11:40,085 --> 01:11:42,421
{\an2}Ambil tasku, Suster! Berikan salibnya!

517
01:11:42,963 --> 01:11:45,841
{\an2}Percikkan air suci di salibnya. Cepat!

518
01:11:45,925 --> 01:11:47,218
{\an2}Cepatlah, Pastor!

519
01:11:49,845 --> 01:11:51,555
{\an2}Tahan dia! Tutup wajahnya!

520
01:11:55,100 --> 01:12:01,106
{\an2}Aku mengusir iblis di dalammu,
demi nama Allah Bapa Yang Maha Kuasa!

521
01:12:01,190 --> 01:12:02,942
{\an2}Dan kuasa Roh Kudus,

522
01:12:03,025 --> 01:12:07,404
{\an2}aku memintanya dalam nama
Bapa kami, Yesus Kristus,

523
01:12:07,488 --> 01:12:10,241
{\an2}yang akan menghakimi
yang hidup dan yang mati,

524
01:12:10,324 --> 01:12:12,910
{\an2}dan dunia yang membara!

525
01:12:30,678 --> 01:12:33,514
{\an2}Itu terasa darurat.

526
01:12:35,432 --> 01:12:36,517
{\an2}Kita terlambat.

527
01:12:37,685 --> 01:12:39,144
{\an2}Iblisnya bebas.

528
01:12:39,436 --> 01:12:40,479
{\an2}Tidak.

529
01:12:41,897 --> 01:12:45,192
{\an2}Iblis harus merasuki jiwa manusia
untuk masuk ke dunia kita.

530
01:12:46,485 --> 01:12:49,572
{\an2}Suster Victoria pasti
biarawati terakhir di tempat ini.

531
01:12:49,655 --> 01:12:51,949
{\an2}- Kau tahu harus berbuat apa.
- Aku tak bisa.

532
01:12:52,032 --> 01:12:53,742
{\an2}Maka Tuhan pun tak bisa menyelamatkan...

533
01:12:58,330 --> 01:12:59,748
{\an2}Itu bukan bunuh diri.

534
01:13:01,500 --> 01:13:03,043
{\an2}<i>Itu pengorbanan...</i>

535
01:13:05,629 --> 01:13:07,506
{\an2}<i>agar iblis tidak mengambil jiwanya.</i>

536
01:13:09,717 --> 01:13:11,969
{\an2}Aku tak mengerti kata-katamu, tapi...

537
01:13:12,469 --> 01:13:16,599
{\an2}kedengarannya penyelidikanmu selesai.
Jadi, ayo kita pergi.

538
01:13:16,682 --> 01:13:17,766
{\an2}Kita tak bisa pergi.

539
01:13:17,850 --> 01:13:20,185
{\an2}Yang benar saja. Kenapa tidak?

540
01:13:22,563 --> 01:13:26,150
{\an2}Kita harus tutup gerbangnya
untuk menahan iblis itu.

541
01:13:33,866 --> 01:13:35,534
{\an2}Gerbangnya ada di katakomba.

542
01:13:36,493 --> 01:13:40,539
{\an2}Kita tak bisa menutupnya tanpa relik itu.
Darah Kristus.

543
01:13:41,749 --> 01:13:43,876
{\an2}"Kristus." Yesus Kristus?

544
01:13:46,086 --> 01:13:47,922
{\an2}Para suster beri tahu ada di mana?

545
01:13:48,255 --> 01:13:50,883
{\an2}Suster Kepala ditemukan tewas
di terowongan ke katakomba.

546
01:13:53,385 --> 01:13:54,720
{\an2}Kurasa aku tahu tempatnya.

547
01:13:55,304 --> 01:13:58,766
{\an2}Bagus. Di situlah pertama kita mencarinya.

548
01:13:59,141 --> 01:14:00,976
{\an2}Tapi sebelum kita mencarinya...

549
01:14:03,729 --> 01:14:05,272
{\an2}aku ingin bersumpah.

550
01:14:07,232 --> 01:14:08,859
{\an2}Kau yakin?

551
01:14:09,902 --> 01:14:11,070
{\an2}Penglihatanku.

552
01:14:11,904 --> 01:14:14,031
{\an2}Kini aku tahu itu mukjizat dari Tuhan.

553
01:14:14,698 --> 01:14:16,617
{\an2}Dan aku siap mengabdi kepada-Nya.

554
01:14:17,451 --> 01:14:19,453
{\an2}Suster, itu baru perbuatan mulia.

555
01:14:20,746 --> 01:14:21,830
{\an2}Sayang sekali, tapi...

556
01:14:23,958 --> 01:14:28,087
{\an2}Dengan otoritas yang diberikan kepadaku,
dan atas nama Gereja...

557
01:14:29,380 --> 01:14:31,507
{\an2}aku menerima sumpah yang kau ambil.

558
01:14:34,510 --> 01:14:36,512
{\an2}Kuserahkan kau kepada Tuhan.

559
01:14:36,929 --> 01:14:42,393
{\an2}Agar persembahan hidupmu menyatu
dengan pengorbanan Ekaristi.

560
01:14:43,102 --> 01:14:44,895
{\an2}Dan dibawa kepada kesempurnaan.

561
01:14:44,978 --> 01:14:50,109
{\an2}Kiranya kasih Tuhan
menyatukanmu selamanya.

562
01:15:14,967 --> 01:15:16,135
{\an2}Tak ada apa-apa di sini.

563
01:15:17,428 --> 01:15:18,512
{\an2}Pasti ada.

564
01:15:19,138 --> 01:15:21,807
{\an2}Mereka bilang kunci ini
membuka pintu ke relik.

565
01:15:22,266 --> 01:15:24,143
{\an2}Bisa di mana saja di kastel ini.

566
01:15:25,894 --> 01:15:29,314
{\an2}Ada di sini. Kau tidak melihatnya, Suster?

567
01:15:30,941 --> 01:15:31,775
{\an2}Apa?

568
01:15:34,820 --> 01:15:36,321
{\an2}Maria menunjukkan jalan.

569
01:16:35,297 --> 01:16:36,757
{\an2}Darah Kristus.

570
01:16:39,134 --> 01:16:40,427
{\an2}Astaga.

571
01:16:42,054 --> 01:16:43,347
{\an2}Yang paling suci.

572
01:16:51,814 --> 01:16:58,195
{\an2}Hanya mempelai Kristus sejati
dapat memegang sesuatu yang sesuci ini.

573
01:17:03,700 --> 01:17:04,660
{\an2}Tunggu.

574
01:17:05,869 --> 01:17:06,829
{\an2}Ada apa?

575
01:17:07,538 --> 01:17:10,541
{\an2}Kita tidak berdoa dulu?

576
01:17:11,416 --> 01:17:14,378
{\an2}Ada waktu untuk berdoa,
ada waktu untuk bertindak, Nak.

577
01:17:14,920 --> 01:17:16,338
{\an2}Sekarang waktunya bertindak.

578
01:17:16,964 --> 01:17:19,967
{\an2}Aku tetap merasa
ini waktunya berdoa, Pastor.

579
01:17:30,227 --> 01:17:33,397
{\an2}<i>"Finit hic, Deo."</i>
Tuhan berakhir di sini.

580
01:17:46,034 --> 01:17:48,871
{\an2}Kita harus menemukan gerbangnya.

581
01:19:05,948 --> 01:19:08,825
{\an2}Suster Irene, lewat sini.

582
01:19:14,039 --> 01:19:14,873
{\an2}Halo?

583
01:19:20,671 --> 01:19:21,880
{\an2}Suster Irene!

584
01:19:23,340 --> 01:19:24,549
{\an2}Suster!

585
01:20:41,543 --> 01:20:42,586
{\an2}Irene!

586
01:21:03,440 --> 01:21:06,985
{\an2}Tuhan Yesus, dalam Nama-Mu yang Kudus,

587
01:21:07,694 --> 01:21:11,114
{\an2}kuikat semua roh jahat ke api ini!

588
01:21:12,074 --> 01:21:15,660
{\an2}Lindungi kami dari iblis
dengan cahaya kudus-Mu!

589
01:21:39,226 --> 01:21:41,770
{\an2}Frenchie. Tolong aku.

590
01:21:45,357 --> 01:21:46,441
{\an2}Tentu.

591
01:23:24,623 --> 01:23:25,749
{\an2}Tidak!

592
01:23:25,832 --> 01:23:27,292
{\an2}Kau gagal.

593
01:23:27,667 --> 01:23:30,629
{\an2}Seperti kau mengecewakan
semua orang dalam hidupmu.

594
01:23:38,178 --> 01:23:41,348
{\an2}Besok, sebuah desa akan kehilangan
orang bodohnya.

595
01:23:42,015 --> 01:23:45,560
{\an2}Seharusnya kau pergi
selagi ada kesempatan, Orang Prancis.

596
01:23:46,520 --> 01:23:48,230
{\an2}Aku Prancis-Kanada.

597
01:23:57,781 --> 01:23:58,823
{\an2}Lari!

598
01:24:01,409 --> 01:24:02,327
{\an2}Frenchie!

599
01:24:05,538 --> 01:24:07,582
{\an2}Tidak!

600
01:24:23,139 --> 01:24:24,391
{\an2}Suster!

601
01:24:25,267 --> 01:24:26,434
{\an2}Suster Irene!

602
01:25:41,009 --> 01:25:44,804
{\an2}Dalam nama Bapa, Putra, dan Roh Kudus.

603
01:27:36,249 --> 01:27:37,709
{\an2}Tidak!

604
01:27:46,342 --> 01:27:47,552
{\an2}Ayo.

605
01:28:06,321 --> 01:28:07,489
{\an2}Baiklah.

606
01:28:18,708 --> 01:28:22,128
{\an2}Kuharap kau tak keberatan.
Namanya "ciuman kehidupan".

607
01:28:23,296 --> 01:28:25,840
{\an2}Namanya memang begitu.
Bukan benar-benar...

608
01:28:25,924 --> 01:28:28,927
{\an2}Frenchie, nama aslimu apa?

609
01:28:30,345 --> 01:28:31,262
{\an2}Maurice.

610
01:28:32,555 --> 01:28:34,849
{\an2}Terima kasih sudah menolongku, Maurice.

611
01:28:36,226 --> 01:28:37,435
{\an2}Sama-sama.

612
01:29:12,887 --> 01:29:14,138
{\an2}Kita harus pergi.

613
01:29:14,597 --> 01:29:17,809
{\an2}Ke tangan-Mu, Ya Tuhan,
kami serahkan hamba-Mu.

614
01:29:18,518 --> 01:29:20,019
{\an2}Para biarawati Saint Carta.

615
01:29:21,229 --> 01:29:24,190
{\an2}Mereka melayani-Mu dalam kehidupan ini
dengan kekuatan dan iman.

616
01:29:25,567 --> 01:29:27,694
{\an2}Kini bebaskanlah mereka dari kejahatan.

617
01:29:28,152 --> 01:29:31,239
{\an2}Biarlah mereka hidup bersama-Mu
dalam anugerah sempurna, selamanya.

618
01:29:32,448 --> 01:29:33,366
{\an2}Amin.

619
01:29:34,951 --> 01:29:36,953
{\an2}Kupikir tanah ini tidak suci lagi.

620
01:29:41,583 --> 01:29:42,750
{\an2}Sekarang sudah suci.

621
01:29:45,461 --> 01:29:46,838
{\an2}Kau tetap tinggal di Biertan?

622
01:29:46,921 --> 01:29:51,342
{\an2}Aku sudah puas dengan Rumania.
